## Third-Party Licenses

This software includes the following third-party packages:

### Production Dependencies

- **chalk** (MIT License) - Terminal string styling
- **commander** (MIT License) - Command-line interface framework
- **fs-extra** (MIT License) - File system utilities
- **node-notifier** (MIT License) - Cross-platform desktop notifications
- **puppeteer** (Apache-2.0 License) - Headless Chrome automation

### Development Dependencies

- **TypeScript** (Apache-2.0 License) - TypeScript compiler
- **Jest** (MIT License) - Testing framework
- **ESLint** (MIT License) - Code linting
- **Prettier** (MIT License) - Code formatting

For complete license information of dependencies, see the respective package documentation.

